{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"🤔️ Jason Yang's Blog","author":"Jason Yang"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"21e7441c-7514-5ecc-b178-1bd478b84088","excerpt":"又偏离航线了，一开始就为了装个黑域，从安装adb到更新homebrew、再到更新ruby，我在瞎折腾的路上无法自拔。。。大概过程是这样\n首先安装android-platform-tools \n这玩意就开始更新，看来我确实很久没用homebrew装软件了。然后蹦出来个这用rvm来管理ruby版本，所以先把rvm…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>又偏离航线了，一开始就为了装个黑域，从安装adb到更新homebrew、再到更新ruby，我在瞎折腾的路上无法自拔。。。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>大概过程是这样\n首先安装android-platform-tools <code class=\"language-text\">brew install android-platform-tools</code>\n这玩意就开始更新，看来我确实很久没用homebrew装软件了。</p>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--java\"><span class=\"syntax--storage syntax--type syntax--java\"><span>Updating</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--storage syntax--type syntax--java\"><span>Homebrew</span></span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--dereference syntax--java\"><span>.</span><span>.</span></span><span>.</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--java\"><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--comparison syntax--java\"><span>==</span><span>&gt;</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--storage syntax--type syntax--java\"><span>Downloading</span></span><span>&nbsp;https</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--ternary syntax--java\"><span>:</span></span><span class=\"syntax--comment syntax--line syntax--double-slash syntax--java\"><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--comment syntax--java\"><span>//</span></span><span>homebrew.bintray.com/bottles-portable/portable-ruby-2.3.3.leopard_64.bottle.1.tar.gz</span></span></span></div></pre></div>\n<p>然后蹦出来个这</p>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--java\"><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--java\"><span>/</span></span><span>usr</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--java\"><span>/</span></span><span>local</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--java\"><span>/</span></span><span class=\"syntax--storage syntax--type syntax--java\"><span>Homebrew</span></span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--java\"><span>/</span></span><span class=\"syntax--storage syntax--type syntax--java\"><span>Library</span></span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--java\"><span>/</span></span><span class=\"syntax--storage syntax--type syntax--java\"><span>Homebrew</span></span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--java\"><span>/</span></span><span>brew</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--dereference syntax--java\"><span>.</span></span><span>rb</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--ternary syntax--java\"><span>:</span></span><span class=\"syntax--constant syntax--numeric syntax--java\"><span>12</span></span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--control syntax--ternary syntax--java\"><span>:</span></span><span>in&nbsp;`</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--comparison syntax--java\"><span>&lt;</span></span><span>main</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--comparison syntax--java\"><span>&gt;</span></span><span class=\"syntax--string syntax--quoted syntax--single syntax--java\"><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--string syntax--begin syntax--java\"><span>&#39;</span></span><span>:&nbsp;Homebrew&nbsp;must&nbsp;be&nbsp;run&nbsp;under&nbsp;Ruby&nbsp;2.3!&nbsp;You</span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--string syntax--end syntax--java\"><span>&#39;</span></span></span><span>re&nbsp;running&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--constant syntax--numeric syntax--java\"><span>2.0</span><span>.0</span></span><span>.&nbsp;</span><span>(</span><span class=\"syntax--storage syntax--type syntax--java\"><span>RuntimeError</span></span><span>)</span></span></div></pre></div>\n<p>用rvm来管理ruby版本，所以先把rvm安装一下，简单3步\n(1)<code class=\"language-text\">curl -L get.rvm.io | bash -s stable</code>\n(2)<code class=\"language-text\">source ~/.profile</code>\n(3)<code class=\"language-text\">source ~/.bash</code></p>\n<p>折腾完看看版本号\n<code class=\"language-text\">rvm -v</code></p>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--text syntax--plain syntax--null-grammar\"><span>rvm&nbsp;1.29.3&nbsp;(latest)&nbsp;by&nbsp;Michal&nbsp;Papis,&nbsp;Piotr&nbsp;Kuczynski,&nbsp;Wayne&nbsp;E.&nbsp;Seguin&nbsp;[</span><span class=\"syntax--markup syntax--underline syntax--link syntax--https syntax--hyperlink\"><span>https://rvm.io</span></span><span>]</span></span></div></pre></div>\n<p>装完rvm，就可以更新ruby了</p>\n<p>可以用<code class=\"language-text\">rvm list known</code>查看一下已发布的版本，我这里安装2.3.4版本</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">rvm install 2.3.4</code></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">ruby -v</code></p>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--text syntax--plain syntax--null-grammar\"><span>ruby&nbsp;2.3.4p301&nbsp;(2017-03-30&nbsp;revision&nbsp;58214)&nbsp;[x86_64-darwin15]</span></span></div></pre></div>\n<p>更新完ruby，再来试试homebrew～</p>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--java\"><span>brew&nbsp;cask&nbsp;install&nbsp;android</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--java\"><span>-</span></span><span>platform</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--java\"><span>-</span></span><span>tools</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--java\"><span>adb&nbsp;devices</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--java\"><span class=\"syntax--storage syntax--type syntax--java\"><span>List</span></span><span>&nbsp;of&nbsp;devices&nbsp;attached</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--java\"><span class=\"syntax--constant syntax--numeric syntax--java\"><span>1164111025</span></span><span>\tunauthorized</span></span></div></pre></div>\n<p>Game Over！</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"mac osx ruby 升级","date":"2017-11-26"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/mac-osx-ruby-upgrade/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/singleton-pattern/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"单例模式"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/change-or-accept/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"不能改变，那就接受"}}}}